    "56b1bed5": {"text":"select the province at screen center.","hash":"h1-d3bb04f8"},
    "56c8071d": {"text":"🕯 {name}, betrothed to your son {child}, has died before the wedding. The dowry returns to your coffers.","hash":"h1-3077a16f"},
    "56e2180f": {"text":"The swarm takes offense and then takes flight.","hash":"h1-c12b64ba"},
    "56f0e3a1": {"text":"📜 The Great Heathen Army sweeps over the English kingdoms.","hash":"h1-68209c9e"},
    "5702af09": {"text":"Your ruling pleases one house and makes an enemy of the other.","hash":"h1-934c9b7b"},
    "57070251": {"text":"The phrasing fixes itself in your mind as if written there.","hash":"h1-24444cfe"},
    "571ef7e1": {"text":"None — this land feeds no duchy or crown.","hash":"h1-f5bed8f1"},
    "574442fd": {"text":"Knowledge that outlives its keepers. (+1 scholarship per season)","hash":"h1-6f86544f"},
    "575b08e1": {"text":"The offer was a test. Your reputation reaches the door before you do.","hash":"h1-d755ffb9"},
    "57686ce1": {"text":"Some doors are better left unknocked.","hash":"h1-e5c810f1"},
    "577a15e9": {"text":"The patron has paid less than half while claiming to have paid all.","hash":"h1-52ceed76"},
    "577f1c3b": {"text":"A Page in the Hall","hash":"h1-ca742b6c"},
    "57a4fec1": {"text":"Work hard and be noticed.","hash":"h1-8375d26d"},
    "57bb1079": {"text":"Press the appeal.","hash":"h1-fb61aa00"},
    "57e3a14d": {"text":"☰ → Settings sets the speed of days.","hash":"h1-669d4b4b"},
    "587b4707": {"text":"You make him laugh, and the toll is forgotten.","hash":"h1-22d9679a"},
    "589276b9": {"text":"The Ford in Flood","hash":"h1-94b9d0f4"},
    "58a835bb": {"text":"Barns and talk. Let them meet.","hash":"h1-e9ff857e"},
    "58b3a6ad": {"text":"A Vassal’s Suit","hash":"h1-74247d57"},
    "58c93d19": {"text":"The lord’s men arrive while your arms are full.","hash":"h1-88c42da2"},
    "58cd41fd": {"text":"the lord","hash":"h1-d3a3d5c7"},
    "58e62c37": {"text":"Bid on the lot. (8 gold)","hash":"h1-2fb6766e"},
    "58eb2491": {"text":"Fever season fills the infirmary. The sick call for water, for prayers, for their mothers.","hash":"h1-7cf6376d"},
    "58f1a011": {"text":"Gone at {age}; the chronicle leaves most of the page blank.","hash":"h1-8a8dfbec"},
    "592deaef": {"text":"No plot within your reach.","hash":"h1-b160424a"},
    "5942a8c3": {"text":"Your quiet work costs {name} dearly, and no one can prove a thing.","hash":"h1-4eb43971"},
    "595060e1": {"text":"Three servants taken in the night; one talks. The paid knife flees your hall ahead of the rope, and the silence lifts.","hash":"h1-343b2403"},
    "59515f99": {"text":"Salvage on the Block","hash":"h1-11c40545"},
    "59542d2d": {"text":"Generosity the powerful remember.","hash":"h1-63119172"},
    "59717a89": {"text":"The lord’s favor is not yet sufficient.","hash":"h1-293c1f54"},
    "5977f041": {"text":"One back bent so the village stands straight.","hash":"h1-836f5a17"},
    "59782391": {"text":"pan the map ·","hash":"h1-a2207924"},
    "598e5647": {"text":"A dying man’s will, carried in your skull.","hash":"h1-9270725e"},
    "59cb7ef1": {"text":"🎓 {tutor} takes charge of {name}’s lessons.","hash":"h1-dca4c134"},
    "59d357b3": {"text":"Charity asked for is charity halved.","hash":"h1-aa32b016"},
    "59d89dcd": {"text":"The old custom is plain enough. The tally closes without your name.","hash":"h1-fdb3f8b4"},
    "59e570a5": {"text":"Mourned by more households than the family admits.","hash":"h1-bddeea23"},
    "5a10bc71": {"text":"The thaw has come and the earth turns soft. What goes into the ground now decides who eats next winter.","hash":"h1-6fb274c8"},
    "5a2ae94d": {"text":"A quiet day, well held, is remembered too.","hash":"h1-671bf2cb"},
    "5a34cb55": {"text":"Counties","hash":"h1-9d4260d3"},
    "5aa3d109": {"text":"🧑‍🏫 A Tutor for {name}","hash":"h1-1174e332"},
    "5aab176f": {"text":"Perfect service is its own recommendation.","hash":"h1-3b41608a"},
    "5ab574a1": {"text":"Doze in the back.","hash":"h1-a816c390"},
    "5af8b769": {"text":"The Family Tree","hash":"h1-38301df4"},
    "5af95171": {"text":"A short purse, politely explained.","hash":"h1-7a370df1"},
    "5b017ec1": {"text":"Survived an assassin!","hash":"h1-506dae8e"},
    "5b02f82f": {"text":"Expose the thief — but slander cuts both ways.","hash":"h1-09c83f90"},
    "5b136e41": {"text":"The old gods remember those who remember them.","hash":"h1-497cc7a9"},
    "5b4c0471": {"text":"Was widowed — suddenly, conveniently.","hash":"h1-60e94651"},
    "5b597539": {"text":"The masters of the craft eat together, set prices together, and bury each other’s dead. A seat at their bench costs silver — and buys a future.","hash":"h1-15f50cd5"},
    "5b5c1757": {"text":"Eastern Christianity","hash":"h1-e247c1c4"},
    "5b90c249": {"text":"Omens are for old women.","hash":"h1-1ebd3dad"},
    "5bb16641": {"text":"Hear the villagers’ grievances.","hash":"h1-8c9ec16d"},
    "5bb3add7": {"text":"You eat dirt in front of the whole village. They cheer anyway.","hash":"h1-9e2e873e"},
    "5bba2519": {"text":"👁 Observe","hash":"h1-c1f39c5b"},
    "5bd33103": {"text":"Glory if the line holds; a wound and ashes if it breaks.","hash":"h1-de700904"},
    "5bd650b9": {"text":"Buy the ringleaders, one by one. (25 gold)","hash":"h1-165d32dd"},
    "5bd9ad75": {"text":"Three knives in the dark, and only your own arm.","hash":"h1-3a50e897"},
    "5bf26841": {"text":"Set straight, splinted, and slow to knit.","hash":"h1-57d9ccdd"},
    "5c006821": {"text":"Iron shares turn the deep clays. (+10% tax)","hash":"h1-05535882"},
    "5c3e8a1b": {"text":"🚩 Muster the host","hash":"h1-0b9a3926"},
    "5c4b15d5": {"text":"★★★★ hard","hash":"h1-01353b22"},
    "5c5582a9": {"text":"The supply wagons are late again, and the host eats the countryside as it goes. A farmstead ahead has full cribs and frightened eyes.","hash":"h1-561ba1b0"},
    "5c7aa431": {"text":"{god} preserve us.","hash":"h1-b2c6bdcb"},
    "5c95f999": {"text":"⚖ {new_liege} takes you as his direct man — {old_liege} is passed over.","hash":"h1-20167edf"},
    "5cca9d81": {"text":"Oil Press","hash":"h1-83d11ae0"},
    "5cf732c1": {"text":"Sound out families for his hand. A pledge binds; the wedding follows at sixteen. (sealing one spends the day)","hash":"h1-25352ca5"},
    "5d103841": {"text":"The household owns:","hash":"h1-1636cdf4"},
    "5d164fa9": {"text":"The shaping is done; the world awaits.","hash":"h1-f9363237"},
