    "5dd88fb7": {"text":"Shift+arrows","hash":"h1-cc891f16"},
    "5de76a3d": {"text":"{lord} reins in beside your warhorse and looks it over far too long. “A fine beast,” he says, “for a common man.”","hash":"h1-24e276ce"},
    "5dee90f1": {"text":"🕊 {realm} goes its own way, released from your fealty.","hash":"h1-1b4135bc"},
