    "5eedc0b9": {"text":"The Moved Stone","hash":"h1-4ed05056"},
    "5ef2aef1": {"text":"A meal and a bed for the night.","hash":"h1-a8fbc762"},
    "5f22ffdf": {"text":"No neighboring lord stands low enough in your liege’s favor ({favor} or less). Time brings disgrace — wait for it.","hash":"h1-aa5ad978"},
    "5f48d50d": {"text":"Emperor","hash":"h1-087766df"},
    "5f5163f9": {"text":"💍 {name} enters your household as your fourth wife.","hash":"h1-663fb09c"},
    "5f5fab2d": {"text":"is a life-and-dynasty game. You begin in 867 AD — most likely poor — and try to raise your family through the ranks of medieval society before old age claims each generation.","hash":"h1-ed29d943"},
    "5f684d9d": {"text":"Maps, candle-stubs, and hard-eyed captains. The war against {enemy} must be given its next move — and the men must see you certain of it.","hash":"h1-14b025b6"},
    "5f7024a5": {"text":"🌷 You begin courting {name}.","hash":"h1-67c954f7"},
    "5f87ecf5": {"text":"💡 Adopt an innovation…","hash":"h1-bc1dd683"},
    "5fd0596d": {"text":"Trade supper for campaign gossip.","hash":"h1-d27b975a"},
