    "61ce997f": {"text":"courting","hash":"h1-d1f3bd20"},
    "61e19e9b": {"text":"💰 Your vassals render {gold} gold in extraordinary taxes — grumbling all the while.","hash":"h1-6e460f48"},
    "61eb0a59": {"text":"Little stock, little profit — but a start.","hash":"h1-f795b2df"},
    "61ef856f": {"text":"The Muster Field","hash":"h1-b5ddf2d6"},
    "61f62fd1": {"text":"You make an enemy for life, and other vassals mutter.","hash":"h1-8dcae611"},
    "62034f91": {"text":"🧑‍🏫 Your tutor","hash":"h1-17aa9ee1"},
    "626add25": {"text":"You misjudge a jest at a great man’s expense. Cold looks follow you to your tent.","hash":"h1-04005233"},
    "62890f31": {"text":"Make him redo it beside you.","hash":"h1-37d55591"},
    "62ab7cbd": {"text":"{rival} has raised a banner, and half the countryside flocks to it — the malcontents, the bought, the bored. Riders in your own colors are seen changing cloaks at the crossroads. There is no more law in this, only spears — or surrender.","hash":"h1-c06149b5"},
    "62b4a331": {"text":"Illness clings to them.","hash":"h1-1d163adc"},
    "62b7d4a5": {"text":"Renounce {liege} and raise your own banner — it means war.","hash":"h1-ce6ea55b"},
    "62bec05d": {"text":"Gossip is a currency too.","hash":"h1-04bfb0f2"},
    "62cdb0b9": {"text":"Sold {childname}’s claim on the house of {late}.","hash":"h1-f629a9ea"},
