    "62fd9f57": {"text":"A concealed tally and a frightened clerk do what righteous speeches could not.","hash":"h1-3d278198"},
    "633482d5": {"text":"You know the roads now, the prices, the men who move goods. Why make one chair when you can sell a hundred?","hash":"h1-3b9bcbba"},
    "6336637d": {"text":"A Dark Night of the Soul","hash":"h1-4d9d7eff"},
    "6356d79f": {"text":"Pay for full confirmation. (12 gold)","hash":"h1-8c824970"},
    "63731463": {"text":"You wed {spouse}, not the whole house.","hash":"h1-5750a399"},
    "637c3021": {"text":"regard {amount}","hash":"h1-e1611b8a"},
    "63906171": {"text":"Declare Independence","hash":"h1-005b7d4d"},
    "63b3f09d": {"text":"Genuinely mourned, which surprised no one more than them.","hash":"h1-f92d4548"},
    "63ca6431": {"text":"Hard labor, and a little peace beside it.","hash":"h1-7519e5dd"},
    "63ed646d": {"text":"Emira","hash":"h1-456f278f"},
    "640d2e09": {"text":"No gold in it, but the priests will remember.","hash":"h1-95b75b7f"},
    "64242ded": {"text":"A Match for {name}","hash":"h1-8030c2ea"},
    "6425627f": {"text":"Deny there was ever another quern.","hash":"h1-0d31853c"},
    "645ca501": {"text":"Allah","hash":"h1-1ae67155"},
    "64657459": {"text":"You are sixteen — grown, in the eyes of {god} and the law. No tutor shaped your years, so what has your family’s household taught you best?","hash":"h1-a29482a8"},
    "646addc5": {"text":"“Spoils of war.” Look away.","hash":"h1-29c89b6c"},
    "6473d855": {"text":"Won a duel of honor.","hash":"h1-53c16ea3"},
    "64813c51": {"text":"Came home from the liege’s war.","hash":"h1-67c429f5"},
    "64def69b": {"text":"📜 Changelog","hash":"h1-1e0fa55e"},
    "64e01e27": {"text":"A debt forgotten is a friend kept.","hash":"h1-fd09e754"},
    "64ec0dc7": {"text":"War Comes to You","hash":"h1-6756adb2"},
    "64f83301": {"text":"🕊 The envoy returns, gifts refused. {realm} is unmoved.","hash":"h1-cede56fa"},
    "655ee82f": {"text":"Keep your edge regardless.","hash":"h1-259be208"},
    "6571b707": {"text":"No coin risked; knowledge travels both ways.","hash":"h1-32c15a2a"},
    "65900225": {"text":"Everything you hold rides on one field.","hash":"h1-1e68c5ea"},
    "65b78fc9": {"text":"I will do the family proud.","hash":"h1-fd0c792a"},
    "65dbfe4d": {"text":"Renew the right already held by your house.","hash":"h1-b72cb67c"},
    "661a4d7f": {"text":"Won freedom in the struggle over the common.","hash":"h1-1639019a"},
    "66231071": {"text":"🏳 The war is done — the host disbands to hearth and field.","hash":"h1-68e58820"},
    "66474ec5": {"text":"The Trap Closes","hash":"h1-544c878c"},
    "665594fd": {"text":"⚔ Drill at arms","hash":"h1-a7d06572"},
    "665dd101": {"text":"Your spear takes the boar before the lord’s. Bold — perhaps too bold. But men saw it.","hash":"h1-27eae6ad"},
    "668924a1": {"text":"{amount} gold","hash":"h1-e0e8ea59"},
    "668bc65d": {"text":"Gates like cliffs, streets like rivers. In {settlement} a fortune is made or lost every day, and nobody asks where you were born — only what you carry.","hash":"h1-4c55bb2b"},
    "66d7d5b3": {"text":"Bought off a rising against the house.","hash":"h1-9d554898"},
    "66daf28d": {"text":"💒 Propose marriage","hash":"h1-5ece8134"},
    "66dbbc2d": {"text":"Gentlewoman","hash":"h1-56638d7e"},
    "672a279f": {"text":"Others’ regard","hash":"h1-056dc6a0"},
    "674f1403": {"text":"Take a fief back from a vassal — by law if he bends, by force if he rises.","hash":"h1-cb81c33a"},
    "67503549": {"text":"Listen, and learn the old tricks.","hash":"h1-37e7178d"},
    "675617ad": {"text":"A cold night’s watch for a warm friend.","hash":"h1-86875a06"},
    "6761a35b": {"text":"Accept the burden.","hash":"h1-448e6264"},
    "6764ed6f": {"text":"Let the beast carry what the road demands.","hash":"h1-49a738ce"},
    "6774ddcf": {"text":"Fight for your seat.","hash":"h1-6c4a5330"},
