    "67c7566b": {"text":"The Pestilence","hash":"h1-d9b91eae"},
    "67c97b29": {"text":"Enfeoff a loyal man with a county — or a whole duchy. Vassals pay taxes, send levies — and remember.","hash":"h1-c04e1675"},
    "67d16845": {"text":"A blessing on the sword. (30 piety)","hash":"h1-dd838d1b"},
