    "8161b149": {"text":"A hasty repair fails inspection. They take food in place of payment.","hash":"h1-3e52ff43"},
    "81866241": {"text":"Serf → Freeholder → Gentry → Baron → Count → Duke → King → Emperor. The Deeds tab always shows a hint for your next step. Wealth, prestige, your lord’s favor, marriage, war-glory, or the church can all raise you.","hash":"h1-66e4be8b"},
    "8186a263": {"text":"The record speaks of another field, or perhaps another village. The case collapses in the reading.","hash":"h1-8324cbe8"},
    "81a0a64d": {"text":"Rush the early cutting.","hash":"h1-505c84f3"},
    "81c15bb1": {"text":"Words, charm, and the ways of court.","hash":"h1-6e8060ef"},
