    "823ca2ad": {"text":"Chronicle","hash":"h1-fc1d518e"},
    "824d68a9": {"text":"Old Widow Hedda’s strips lie fallow since her sons died. Her price is fair, and freehold land is the root of every fortune.","hash":"h1-ada5746b"},
    "827f7d41": {"text":"Unravel their witnesses before yours unravel.","hash":"h1-65d5ff75"},
    "8298639f": {"text":"The lord orders you flogged in the yard as a lesson.","hash":"h1-bede225c"},
    "82cafb7d": {"text":"One word, and {rival} falls — if the web holds.","hash":"h1-8b9788e8"},
    "82df7161": {"text":"Stand between her and the closed ranks.","hash":"h1-1d43527d"},
    "82e2e20d": {"text":"Yield the lands and flee abroad with what you can carry.","hash":"h1-5d2f265b"},
    "830ba9b1": {"text":"A slow market day. You barely cover the road.","hash":"h1-9c72947d"},
