    "8b803dc7": {"text":"No plot in motion.","hash":"h1-f15f3e50"},
    "8b847859": {"text":"The poisoner walks into it, and under questioning gives up a name. The knives stop — and {rival} knows that you know.","hash":"h1-040cc781"},
    "8b8df4c5": {"text":"Somewhere, ink remembers what men deny.","hash":"h1-308df39a"},
    "8b936831": {"text":"Long hours shared with {friend} — work, jokes, a water-skin passed back and forth — have become something like brotherhood.","hash":"h1-2fe66cb1"},
    "8ba40e95": {"text":"Turn victory into a step up the ladder.","hash":"h1-31f24adf"},
    "8bb2fa83": {"text":"Purge the household.","hash":"h1-a8027bb8"},
    "8bbb2a41": {"text":"The Sea Gives","hash":"h1-c4ceec69"},
    "8bd560ff": {"text":"Take it out of his hide.","hash":"h1-55122e2e"},
    "8c0f43f1": {"text":"They are harder men than farmers. You carry home a wound.","hash":"h1-3d27cf21"},
