    "d4da66e1": {"text":"Sayyida","hash":"h1-8b884951"},
    "d4e9be41": {"text":"Press on for {target}.","hash":"h1-839fe4d2"},
    "d4ee0441": {"text":"Bind the right to every hearth.","hash":"h1-0d8a3a99"},
    "d4fc0e69": {"text":"Sell sweets and sherbet to the crowd.","hash":"h1-105bbaeb"},
    "d511a3b1": {"text":"The honest work you know, and nothing more.","hash":"h1-3b62dde7"},
    "d532ade1": {"text":"Another man’s will is another man’s burden.","hash":"h1-c47f443d"},
    "d53ed397": {"text":"Quick of wit, and quicker to mention it.","hash":"h1-758af77c"},
    "d56b420f": {"text":"Granted a barony — a lord at last!","hash":"h1-c08e583a"},
    "d56d1879": {"text":"Now my true education begins.","hash":"h1-9fddc957"},
    "d575c669": {"text":"Watch others gamble.","hash":"h1-bd6a885d"},
    "d5955c41": {"text":"Georgian","hash":"h1-bc5f7fa3"},
    "d59c2541": {"text":"Walk away from luck that glances over its shoulder.","hash":"h1-a0b6ef79"},
    "d5b7f7d3": {"text":"Old soldiers’ tales are lessons in disguise.","hash":"h1-af6a554e"},
    "d5d121fb": {"text":"The scheme unravels, and fingers point at you.","hash":"h1-82c11cc8"},
    "d6089275": {"text":"Silver Ring","hash":"h1-488795da"},
    "d619c351": {"text":"You are {name}, a student of the madrasa of {province}. Ink, memory, and the law can raise a nobody higher than any sword — and unlike the Christians’ monks, a scholar may yet marry and found a house.","hash":"h1-f045cc10"},
    "d62f0441": {"text":"Your mother","hash":"h1-7e35e319"},
    "d646db79": {"text":"Imam","hash":"h1-d460f0d5"},
    "d65809e1": {"text":"Great {temple}","hash":"h1-d4975bd6"},
    "d66cb573": {"text":"Where were you born?","hash":"h1-9080234a"},
    "d67bc331": {"text":"Stubborn, surefooted, profitable.","hash":"h1-9db70b5a"},
    "d6905065": {"text":"🎓 Choose their education focus…","hash":"h1-746912a3"},
    "d6941f39": {"text":"hardier","hash":"h1-a6f0f3d4"},
    "d6948dc5": {"text":"The {holy} traces letters in the dust with a stick and looks at you expectantly. Few children are offered even this much.","hash":"h1-8092f879"},
    "d6a5b50b": {"text":"— your liege","hash":"h1-278bd0b4"},
    "d6a5bee1": {"text":"Words That Linger","hash":"h1-a722b44a"},
    "d6ceec45": {"text":"Stone Bridge","hash":"h1-b9a2cb1b"},
    "d715a457": {"text":"The fields kept, and so did you.","hash":"h1-dec353e6"},
    "d72a6969": {"text":"A fat harvest! Granaries groan, and there is a surplus to sell.","hash":"h1-539a32c3"},
    "d735cb81": {"text":"Leaves no children; the gossips needed no invitation.","hash":"h1-56ffff62"},
    "d7367ab1": {"text":"⚜ {name}: you hold the majority, {held}.","hash":"h1-7eabdb85"},
    "d73a2483": {"text":"A Partner from Far Off","hash":"h1-8405139a"},
    "d74ae10d": {"text":"Through the din you see it: {lord} down, horse screaming, enemies closing like crows. No one else is near enough. You are.","hash":"h1-d9da6e3a"},
    "d75c273d": {"text":"Piety","hash":"h1-cdbf3d86"},
    "d76fc441": {"text":"Festival Day","hash":"h1-7f77f843"},
    "d7739805": {"text":"Sweetened water, if no one tastes the difference.","hash":"h1-17795e20"},
    "d7772ad1": {"text":"Pay him. (8 gold)","hash":"h1-b6982944"},
    "d78f1341": {"text":"🕯 Your grandson {name} has died, aged {age}.","hash":"h1-8adf664f"},
    "d7967741": {"text":"Be seen, be useful, be remembered.","hash":"h1-250d7ac9"},
    "d79f85f1": {"text":"Ask for the patter of small feet.","hash":"h1-7b0f3996"},
    "d7acfa21": {"text":"Court Physicians","hash":"h1-a86477c1"},
    "d7af7103": {"text":"Turn the hall against a man in your way and take his place in the lord’s regard.","hash":"h1-8a40a76c"},
    "d7d98ba1": {"text":"PgUp/PgDn","hash":"h1-baeee7ed"},
    "d7eb4e41": {"text":"Your old master dies with a commission unfinished, debts in the ledger, and a widow facing men who have already begun measuring the workshop.","hash":"h1-0f1671e2"},
    "d7f51e01": {"text":"worth ~{gold} gold","hash":"h1-cceb292d"},
    "d7fa06f7": {"text":"Beg sanctuary of the {temple}.","hash":"h1-d75ac88f"},
    "d800c42b": {"text":"Well-wishers bring gifts to the new couple — a pig, a bolt of cloth, a few coins pressed into your palm.","hash":"h1-ae2ae1e2"},
    "d80cc7b1": {"text":"+ h +","hash":"h1-b10f3fdf"},
    "d83aefef": {"text":"🎓 Hire a learned master (25 gold)","hash":"h1-c3885cb4"},
    "d8712f01": {"text":"The reeve bangs on doors at dawn: {lord} requires labor — hauling stone, mending the mill-race, digging ditches.","hash":"h1-abf044ec"},
    "d8876581": {"text":"Foreign, not false — and worth slightly more than either of you knew.","hash":"h1-d462fa8e"},
    "d8927009": {"text":"You pin the miller’s enormous son to roars of delight.","hash":"h1-57bb4d55"},
