    "db4bfbe5": {"text":"The village children divide into two armies with stick-swords and hurdle-shields. Someone must lead the charge.","hash":"h1-d0cc1938"},
    "db586b81": {"text":"The master mason waits — a quarter off your next work.","hash":"h1-ed9cf909"},
